lead_paragraph: Chelsea scored the fastest goal in the Premier League this season when Brazilian Kenedy's fine left-foot strike after 39 seconds helped secure a 2-1 win over relegation-threatened Norwich City at Carrow Road on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Chelsea's Kenedy Scores After 39 Seconds to Help Sink Norwich
